hadiths[35]{hadithnumber,text}:
1005,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pani ki dua karne ke liye tashrif le gaey aur apni chadar ultai.
1006,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab sar Mubarak aakhiri rakaat (ke rukoo ( se uthatey to yun farmaatey اللهم أنج Ayash بن أبي ربيعة ، Mina padhi. اللهم أنج سلمة بن هشام ، Mina padhi. اللهم أنج الوليد بن الوليد ، Mina padhi. اللهم أنج المستضعفين من المؤمنين ، Mina padhi. اللهم اشدد وطأتك على مضر ، Mina padhi. اللهم اجعلها سنين كسني يوسفke ya Allah ! Ayaash-bin-Abii Rabee ko nijat de. ya Allaah! Salma-bin-Hishaam ko nijat de. ya Allaah! Waleed-bin-Waleed ko nijat de. ya Allah ! be-bas kamzor musalmanon ko nijat de. ya Allaah! Muzar ke kaafiron ko sakht pakad. ya Allah ! unke saal Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke se saal kar de. aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Ghifaar ki qaum ko Allah ne bakhsh diya aur Aslam ki qaum ko Allah ne salamat rakha. ibne-abii-Zanaad ne apne bap se subah ki Namaz mein yahi dua naql ki.
1007,"ham Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein baithey huey they. aap ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab kuffaare-Quraish ki sarkashi dekhi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baddua ki) اللهم سبع كسبع يوسف (ke aey Allah ! saat (7) baras ka qahat un par bhej jaisey Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke waqt mein bheja tha chunanche aisa qahat padaa ke har cheez tabah ho gaee aur logon ne chamdey aur murdar tak kha liye. bhook ki shiddat ka ye aalim tha ke aasman ki taraf nazar uthai jati to dhuein ki tarah malum hota tha aakhir majbur ho kar Abu-Sufiyan haazire-khidmat huey aur arz kya ke aey Muhammad (sl)! aap logon ko Allah ki itaat aur sila-rehmii ka hukm detey hain. ab to aap hi ki qaum barbad ho rahi hai, isliye aap Allah se unke haq mein dua keejiye. Allah Taala ne farmaya ke us din ka intizar kar jab aasman saaf dhuaan nazar aaeyga aayat (انکم عائدون) tak (yahaan tak ki) jab ham sakhti se unki giraft karengey (kuffaar ki) sakht giraft badr ki ladai mein hui. dhuein ka bhi mamla guzar chuka (jab sakht qahat padaa tha) jis mein pakad aur qaid ka zikr hai wo sab ho chukey isi tarah sura Rome ki aayat mein jo zikr hai wo bhi ho chukaa."
1008,maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko abu-Taalib ka ye sher padhtey suna tha ( tarjama ( goraa unka rang unke munh ke waaste se barish ki (Allah se) dua ki jati hai. yatimon ki panah aur bewaon ke sahaarey.''
1009,"aksar mujhey shaair ( abu-Taalib (ka sher yad aa jata hai. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh ko dekh raha tha ke aap dua istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) (baarish ki dua member par) kar rahe they aur abhi (dua'a se farigh ho kar) utrey bhi nahi they ke tamam naley bhar gaey. ( وأبيض يستسقى الغمام بوجهه ثمال اليتامى عصمة للأرامل ( ) tarjama ( goraa rang unka , wo haami yatimon aur bewaon ke log unke munh ke sadqey se pani maangtey hain."
1010,jab kabhi umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamane mein qahat padta to umr (Raziallahu anhu) Abbaas-bin-abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ke waseele se dua kartey aur farmatey ke aey Allah ! pahley ham terey paas apne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka waseela laya kartey they. to to pani barsata tha. ab ham apne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chacha ko waseela banatey hain to to ham par pani barsa . Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke chunanche barish khub hi barsi.
1011,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) (paani barasne ki dua) ki to apni chadar ko bhi ultaa.
1012,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidgaah gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahan duaaey istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) qibley ki taraf ho kar ki aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chadar bhi paltii aur 2 rakaat Namaz padhi. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( kehtey hain ke ibne-Uena kehtey they ke) hadis ke rawi Abdullah-bin-Zaid ( wahi hain jinhoney azan khuwab mein dekhi thi lekin ye unki ghalati hai kyonke ye Abdullah ibne-Zaid-bin-Aasim maazini hai jo Ansar ke qabila maazin se they.
1013,"aap ne aik shakhs ( Kab bin Murra ya Abu-Sufiyan (ka zikr kya jo member ke samney waley darwazey se Juma ke din masjide-Nabawi mein aaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey khutba de rahe they, usne bhi khadey khadey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ya Rasulullah ! ( barish na honey se) janwar mar gaey aur rastey band ho gaey aap Allah Taala se barish ki dua farmaiye. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye kehtey hi hath utha diye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki اللهم اسقنا ‏‏‏‏ ‏‏‏‏اللهم اسقنا ‏‏‏‏ اللهم اسقنا ke aey Allaah! hamein sairaab kar. aey Allah ! hamein sairaab kar. aey Allah ! hamein sairaab kar. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha b-khudaa kahin door door tak aasman par badal ka koi tukda nazar nahi aata tha aur na koi aur cheez (hawa wghaira, jis se malum ho ke barish aaeygii (aur hamarey aur Sala pahaad ke beech koi makan bhi na tha (ke ham badal honey ke bawajud na dekh saktey hon) pahaad ke peechhey se dhaal ke barabar badal namudaar hua aur beech aasman tak pahunch kar charon taraf phail gaya aur barish shuru ho gaee, Allah ki qasam! ham ne suraj aik hafte tak nahi dekha. phir aik shakhs doosrey Juma ko usi darwazey se aaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey khutba de rahe they, us shakhs ne phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khadey-khadey hi mukhaatab kya ke ya Rasulullah! (baarish ki kasarat se) maal w manaal par tabahi aa gaee aur rastey band ho gaey. Allah Taala se dua kijiye ke barish rok de. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hath uthaey aur dua ki اللهم حوالينا wla علينا ، Mina padhi. اللهم على الآكام والجبال والآجام والظراب والأودية ومنابت الشجرke ya Allah ab hamarey ird-gird barish barsaa, ham se usey rok de. teelon, pahaadon, pahaadiyon, wadiyon aur baaghon ko sairaab kar. unhon-ne kaha ke us dua se barish khatm ho gaee aur ham nikley to dhoop nikal chuki thi. Sharik ne kaha ke maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke ye wahi pahlaa shakhs tha to unhon-ne farmaya ke mujhey malum nahi."
1014,"aik shakhs Juma ke din masjid mein dakhil hua. ab jahan daarul-qazaa hai usi taraf ke darwazey se wo aaya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey khutba de rahe they, usne bhi khadey khadey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mukhaatab kya kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! janwar mar gaey aur rastey band ho gaey. Allah Taala se dua kijiye ke ham par pani barsaey . chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon hath utha kar dua farmai ( اللهم أغثنا , Mina padhi. اللهم أغثنا , Mina padhi. اللهم أغثنا (aey Allah ! ham par pani barsa . aey Allah ! hamein sairaab kar. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Allah ki qism ! aasman par badal ka kahin nishan bhi na tha aur hamarey aur Sala pahaad ke beech mein makanon bhi nahi they, itney mein pahaad ke peechhey se badal namudaar hua dhaal ki tarah aur aasman ke beech mein pahunch kar charon taraf phail gaya aur barasney laga. Allah ki qism ! ham ne aik hafte tak suraj nahi dekha. phir doosrey Juma ko aik shakhs usi darwazey se dakhil hua. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey khutba de rahe they, isliye usne khadey-khadey kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! ( kasarate-baarish se) janwar tabah ho gaey aur rastey band ho gaey. Allah Taala se dua kijiye ke barish band ho jaaey. rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon hath utha kar dua ki اللهم حوالينا wla علينا ، Mina padhi. اللهم على الآكام والظراب وبطون الأودية ومنابت الشجرaey Allah ! hamarey aas-paas mein barish barsa (jahaan zarurat hai) ham par na barsa. aey Allah ! teelon pahaadiyon wadiyon aur baaghon ko sairaab kar. chunanche barish ka silsile band ho gaya aur ham bahar aaey to dhoop nikal chuki thi. Sharik ne bayan kya ke maine Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se malum kya ke kya ye pahlaa hi shakhs tha? unhon-ne jawab diya mujhey malum nahi."
1015,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Juma ke din khutba de rahe they ke aik shakhs aaya aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! pani ka qahat pad gaya hai, Allah se dua kijiye ke hamein sairaab kar de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki aur barish is tarah shuru hui ke gharon tak pahunchnaa mushkil ho gaya, doosrey Juma tak barabar barish hoti rahi. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir (doosrey Juma mein) wahi shakhs ya koi aur khada hua aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! dua kijiye ke Allah Taala barish ka rukh kisi aur taraf mod de. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmai ke) اللهم حوالينا wla علينا (aey Allah hamarey ird-gird barish barsa ham par na barsa . Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine dekha ke badal tukdey tukdey ho kar daain baain taraf chaley gaey phir wahan barish shuru ho gaee aur Madina mein iska silsile band hua."
1016,"aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ke janwar halaak ho gaey aur rastey band ho gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki aur aik hafte tak barish hoti rahi phir aik shakhs aaya aur arz kya ke) barish ki kasarat se) ghar gir gaey rastey band ho gaey. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir khadey ho kar dua ki اللهم على الآكام والظراب والأودية ومنابت الشجرke aey Allah ! barish teelon , pahadon , wadiyon aur baaghon mein barsa ( dua ke nateeja mein) badal Madina se is tarah phat gaey jaisey kapda phat kar tukdey tukdey ho jata hai."
1017,"aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. kaha ya Rasulullah (sl)! janwar halaak ho gaey aur rastey band ho gaey. aap Allah Taala se dua keejiye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmai to aik Juma se doosrey Juma tak barish hoti rahi phir doosrey Juma ko aik shakhs haazire-khidmat hua aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! (bahut zyada barish hone se) makanon gir gaey, rastey band ho gaey aur maweshii halaak ho gaey. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmaaii اللهم على رءوس الجبال والآكام وبطون الأودية ومنابت الشجرke aey Allah ! pahadon teelon wadiyon aur baghaat ki taraf barish ka rukh kar de. ( jahan barish ki kami hai) chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dua se badal kapdey ki tarah phat gaya."
1018,aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (qahat se) maal ki barbadi aur ahal w ayaal ki bhook ki shikayat ki. chunaanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne duaaey istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) ki. rawi ne us mauqe par na chadar palatney ka zikr kya aur na qible ki taraf munh karne kaa.
1019,"aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. arz kya ya Rasulullah! (qahat se) janwar halaak ho gaey aur rastey band, Allah se dua keejiye. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki aur aik Juma se agley Juma tak aik hafta barish hoti rahi. phir aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! ( barish ki kasarat se) rastey band ho gaey aur jaanwar halaak ho gaey. ab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye dua ki  اللهم على ظهور الجبال والآكام وبطون الأودية ومنابت الشجرke aey Allah ! barish ka rukh pahaadon, teelon, wadiyon aur baghaat ki taraf mod de. chunaanche badal Madina se is tarah chhat gaya jaisey kapda phat jaya karta hai."
1020,"mein ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir tha. aap ne farmaya ke Quraish ka Islam se munh phernaa badhtaa gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke haq mein baddua ki. us baddua ke nateejey mein aisa qahat padaa ke kuffaar marney lagey aur murdar aur haddiyaan khaney lagey. aakhir Abu-Sufiyan aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya aey Muhammad! (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aap sila rehmii ka hukm detey hain lekin aap ki qaum mar rahi hai. izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah se dua keejiye. aap ne us aayat ki tilawat ki (tarjama) us din ka intizar kar jab aasman par saaf khula hua dhuaan namudaar hoga. (khair aap ne dua ki barish hui qahat jata raha) lekin wo phir kufr karne lagey is par Allah paak ka ye farman nazil hua (tarjama) jis din ham unhein sakhti ke sath pakad karengey aur ye pakad badr ki ladai mein hui aur asbaat-bin-Muhammad ne Mansoor se bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne duaaey istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) ki (Madina mein) jiske nateeje mein khub barish hui ke saat (7) din tak wo barabar jari rahi. aakhir logon ne barish ki zyadti ki shikayat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki (اللهم حوالينا wla علينا) ke aey Allah ! hamarey aas-paas barish barsaa, Madina mein barish ka silsile khatm kar. chunanche badal aasman se chhat gaya aur Madina ke ird-gird khub barish hui."
1021,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Juma ke din khutba de rahe they ke itney mein logon ne khadey ho kar shor machaayaa, kehney lagey ke ya Rasulullah! barish ke naam boond bhi nahi darakht surkh ho chukey (yani tamam pattey khushk ho gaey) aur janwar tabah ho rahe hain, aap Allah Taala se dua kijiye ke hamein sairaab kare. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki (اللهم اسقنا) aey Allaah! hamein sairaab kar. 2 martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is tarah kaha, qism Allah ki us waqt aasman par badal kahin door-door nazar nahi aata tha lekin dua ke baad achcha aik badal aaya aur barish shuru ho gaee. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member se utarey aur Namaz padhai. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey to barish ho rahi thi aur doosrey Juma tak barish barabar hoti rahi phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) doosrey Juma mein khutbe ke liye khadey huey to logon ne bataya ke makanon gir gaey aur rastey band ho gaey, Allah se dua kijiye ke barish band kar de. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraaey aur dua ki) االلهم حوالينا wla علينا (aey Allah ! hamarey aas-paas mein ab barish barsa , Madina mein iska silsile band kar. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dua se Madina se badal chhat gaey aur barish hamarey aas-paas honey lagi us shaan se ke ab Madina mein aik boond bhi na padti thi maine Madina ko dekha abr taaj ki tarah aas-paas tha aur Madina iske beech mein."
1022,"Abdullah-bin Yazeed Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) paani barasney ke liye bahar nikley. unke sath Bara-bin-Aazib aur Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. unhon-ne pani ke liye dua ki to paon par khadey rahe, member na tha. isi tarah aap ne dua ki phir 2 rakaat Namaz padhi jis mein qirat buland awaz se ki, na azan kahi aur na iqamat Abu-Ishaq ne kaha Abdullaah-bin-Yazeed ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha tha."
1023,"unke chacha Abdullah-bin-Zaid ne jo sahabi they, unhein khabar di ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ko sath lekar istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) ke liye nikley aur aap khadey huey aur khadey hi khadey Allah Taala se dua ki, phir qible ki taraf munh karke apni chadar paltii chunanche barish khub hui."
1024,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) ke liye bahar nikley to qible ki taraf ho kar dua ki. phir apni chadar paltii aur 2 rakaat Namaz padhi. Namaz mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qirat buland awaz se ki.
1025,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) ke liye bahar nikley, dekha tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni peeth sahaba ki taraf kar di aur qibla rukh ho kar dua ki. phir chadar paltii aur 2 rakaat Namaz padhai jiski aap ne awaz ke sath qirat ki thi."
1026,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne duaaey istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) ki to 2 rakaat Namaz padhi aur chadar paltii.
1027,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) duaaey istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) ke liye eidgaah ko nikley aur qibla rukh ho kar do rakaat Namaz padhi phir chadar paltii. Sufiyan Sory ne kaha mujhey Abdur-Rehman bin-Abdullah Mas'oodii ne Abu-Bakar ke hawale se khabar di ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chadar ka daahinaa kona baain kandhey par dala.
1028,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) ke liye) eidgaah ki taraf nikley wahan Namaz padhney ko jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dua karne lagey ya rawi ne ye kaha dua ka irada kya to qible ki taraf ho kar chadar paltii. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( kehtey hain ke us hadis ke rawi Abdullah-bin-Zaid maazini hain aur us se pahley baab ( الدعا فی الاستسقاء ( mein jinka zikr guzra aur wo Abdullaah-bin-Yazeed hain Kufa ke rehney waale.
1029,"aik badwi (gaaun ka rehney wala) Juma ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur arz kya ya Rasulullah! bhook se maweshii tabah ho gaey, ahal w ayaal aur tamam log mar rahe hain. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hath uthaaey, aur logon ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath apne hath uthaaey, dua karne lagey, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke abhi ham masjid se bahar nikley bhi na they ke barish shuru ho gaee aur aik hafta barabar barish hoti rahi. doosrey Juma mein phir wahi shakhs aaya aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah! (baarish bahut honey se) musaafir ghabraa gaey aur rastey band ho gaey."
1030,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ne istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) mein dua karne ke liye) is tarah hath uthaey ke maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baghlon ki safedi dekh li.
1031,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) duaaey istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) ke siwa aur kisi dua ke liye hath (zyaada) nahi uthatey they aur istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) mein hath itna uthatey ke baghlon ki safedi nazar aa jati.
1032,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab barish hoti dekhtey to ye dua kartey (صيبا نافعا) aey Allah ! nafa bakhshney wali barish barsa. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Qaasim-bin-Yahyaa ne Ubaidullah Umri se ki hai aur uski riwayat Auzai aur Aqeel ne Naafe se ki hai.
1033,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein logon par aik baar qahat padaa. unhi dinon Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Juma ke din member par khutba de rahe they ke aik dehati ne khadey ho kar kaha ya Rasulullah! janwar mar gaey aur baal-bachchey faaqey par faaqey kar rahe hain, Allah Taala se dua kijiye ke pani barsaey. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye sun kar dua ke liye donon hath utha diye. aasman par door-door tak abr ka pata tak nahi tha. lekin (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dua se) pahadon ke barabar badal garajtey huey aagey abhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member se utrey bhi nahi they ke maine dekha ke barish ka pani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dadhi se bah raha hai. Anas ne kaha ke us roz barish din bhar hoti rahi. doosrey din teesrey din, bhi aur barabar isi tarah hoti rahi. is tarah doosra Juma aa gaya. phir yahi badwi ya koi doosra shakhs khada hua aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah (sl)! (baarish ke zyada hone se) Imaaratein gir gain aur janwar doob gaey, hamarey liye Allah Taala se dua kijiye . chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir donon hath uthaey aur dua ki) اللهم حوالينا wla علينا (ke aey Allaah! hamarey aaspaas mein barsa aur ham par na barsa. Anas ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne hathon se aasman ki jis taraf bhi ishara kar detey abr idhar se phat jata, ab Madina hauz ki tarah bin chuka tha aur usi ke baad wadi qanaa ka naala aik mahina tak bahtaa raha. Anas ne bayan kya ke iske baad Madina ke aaspaas se jo bhi aaya usne khub sairaabii ki khabar sunai."
1034,jab tez hawa chaltii to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak par dar mehsus hota tha.
1035,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey purwaa hawa ke zariey madad pahunchai gaee aur qaume-aad pachhwaa ke zariey halaak kar di gaee thi.
1036,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat us waqt tak na aaeygii jab tak ilme-deen na uth jaeyga aur zalzalon ki kasarat na ho jaeygi aur zamana jaldi-jaldi na guzrey ga aur fitney-fasaad phoot padengey aur) هرج ( ki kasarat ho jaeygi aur) هرج ( se murad qatl hai. qatl aur tumharey darmyan daulat w maal ki itni kasarat hogi ke wo ubal padega.
1037,farmaya aey Allaah! hamarey Sham (Syria) aur Yaman par barkat nazil farmaa. is par logon ne kaha aur hamarey Najad ke liye bhi barkat ki dua kijiye lekin aap ne phir wahi kaha ''aey Allaah! hamarey Sham (Syria) aur Yaman par barkat naazil farma'' phir logon ne kaha aur hamarey Najad mein? to aap ne farmaya ke wahan to zalzale aur fitney hongey aur shaitan ka seeng wahi se tuloo hoga.
1038,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hudaibiya mein ham ko subah ki Namaz padhai. raat ko barish ho chuki thi Namaz ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya malum hai tumharey rab ne kya faisla kya hai? log boley ke Allah Taala aur uske rasool khub jantey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke parwardigar farmata hai aaj mere 2 tarah ke bandon ne subah ki. aik momin hai aik kaafir. jisne kaha Allah ke Fazal w raham se pani padaa wo to mujh par eman laya aur sitaron ka munkir hua aur jisne kaha falan taarey ke falan jagah aaney se pani padaa usne mera kufr kya, taaron par eman laya."
1039,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghaib ki panch kunjiyaan hain jinhein Allah Taala ke siwa aur koi nahi janta. kisi ko nahi malum ke kal kya honey wala hai, koi nahi janta ke maa ke pet mein kya hai, kal kya karna hoga, iska kisi ko ilm nahi. na koi ye janta hai ke usey maut kis jagah aaeygi aur na kisi ko ye malum ke barish Kab hogi."
